author: stefan2
msg: On the 10Gb branch: instead of variable length keys use fixed length
structs as keys for the revprop and fulltext caches.  Those keys
don't require intermediate strings to be constructed and are faster
to process on the cache side.
(pair_cache_key_t): declare a rather generic key type
(svn_fs_fs__initialize_caches): init caches with fixed key lengths
svn_fs_fs__try_process_file_contents): use the new key type
